  U7 chit8-jit8 koat-teng7 bin5-a2-jit8 beh to3-khi3, chiu7 koh choe3-hoe2 khi3 ban2 pek-hap8-hoe, kau3 ti7 soaN-nih e5 toa7 chhiu7 kha, u7 chit8-te3 toa7 chioh8 chheng-khi3 chheng-khi3, Khun-hong chiu7 chiong i ka-ti7 e5 chhiu2-kin-a2 thi2-khui chhu ti7 chioh8-thau5 teng2, khan Hui7-bi2 e5 chhiu2 chhiaN2 i che7. Hui7-bi2 chiu7 che7, i ka-ti7 ia7 che7 ti7 Hui7-bi2 e5 sin-piN. Hian2-chhut ban7-hun e5 chhin-chhiat chhio3-iong5 e5 bin7 tui3 Hui7-bi2 kong2 ¡§Hui7-bi2 sio2-chia2, goa2 tui3 li2 chin sit-le2, goa2 siuN7 beh tui3 li2 kong2 chit8-ku3 oe7, na7-si7 chin tiu-tu5 kong2 long2 be7 chhut--lai5, m7-chai...... m7-chai...... ?¡¨ Hui7-bi2 khoaN3 i thun-thun thou3-thou3 i-ni ng3-nngh8, chiu7 ho2-i3 ka7 i kong2 ¡§Beh thai2 u7 sim2-mih8 sit-le2, li2 lai5, goan2 chin siu7 an-ui3, chin hoaN-hi2 li2 e5 pang-bang5, goan2 eng-kai ka7 li2 seh-sia7, na2-li2 u7 sit-le2 e5 sou2-chai7.¡¨ ¡§M7-si7 an2-ni lah, si7 goa2 chit-si5 beh ka7 li2 kong2 chit8 ku3 oe7, tui3 li2 khah sit-le2, goa2 si7 ng3-bang7 li2 m7-thang siu7-khi3.¡¨ ¡§Be7-be7, chhiaN2 li2 kong2, bo5-lun7 li2 kong2 sim2-mih8 goa2 to be7 siu7-khi3, chhiaN2 li2 an-sim.¡¨ Tui3 an2-ni Khun-hong chiu7 chin an-sim, khan Hui7-bi2 e5 chhiu2 khi2-lai5 chim, ia7 ka7 i kong2 ¡§Hui7 moai7-moai7 goa2 sit8-chai7 chin thiaN3 li2, goa2 ng3-bang7 e7-tit eng2-oan2 thiaN3--li2.......¡¨ Hui7-bi2 thiaN chit ku3 oe7 sim hut-jian5 kam2-kak chin kin2-tiong, tan7-si7 bo5 chek-si5 in3--i, chiu7 aN3-io eng7 cheng2-thau5-a2 oe7 ti7 thou5-kha e5 thou5-soa teng2, oe7 chit8 boe2 hi5, Khun-hong khoaN3 hit e5 hi5 e5 tou5, sim chin hoaN-hi2, i e5 i3-su3 si7 kong2 Hui7-bi2 in2--i, piau2-si7 nng7-lang5 saN tek-i3 si7 chhin-chhiuN7 hi5 tit-tioh8 chui2 e5 hoaN-hi2. Ki5-sit8 m7-si7, na7-si7 Khun-hong bo5 beng5 hit e5 i3-su3, chiu7 koh tit8-tit8 kong2 chin che7 ho2-i3 e5 oe7. Ti3-kau3 Hui7-bi2 put-tek-i2 chiu7 koh aN3-io eng7 cheng2-thau5-a2 oe7 sip8-ji7-ke3 e5 ki3-ho7. Hit-si5 i chiah hut-jian5 hiau2-ngou7, chai Hui7-bi2 oe7 ¡§Hi5,¡¨ oe7 ¡§Sip8-ji7-ke3¡¨ long2 si7 piau2-hian7 i si7 Ki-tok-tou5. Bo5 sui5-pian7 beh kap bi7-sin3-chia2 kiat-hun. Na7-si7 Khun-hong e5 sim si7 chin-chhiat e5 kiu5-ai3. Kou-put-chiong Hui7-bi2 chiu7 theng5-sin khi2--lai5 eng7 chin giam5-siok tai7-hong e5 khoan2-sit, lau2-lau2 sit8-sit8 ka7 i kong2. 
