  Kong2 Khun-hong to-si7 toa7-oh8 pit8-giap8, koh siong-tong e5 ka-teng5. Ka-ti7 su7-giap8 ia7 seng5-kong, an2-choaN2 e7 kau3 27 hoe3 iau2-boe7 chhoa7, che si7 chit8 e5 chin-chhim e5 goan5-in, bo5 kong2 lin2 long2 m7-chai. Goan5-in si7 Khun-hong e5 lau7-pe7 cha2-si5 choe3 koaN se3-ka-te2, na7-si7 kho2-sioh cha2-si2. Lau7-bu2 si7 chit8 e5 bu2-koaN chin u7 se3-lek8 e5 chiong-kun thoan5-tiuN2 e5 sio2-moai7. Tiong7-hu si2 liau2 chiu7 chiuN2 chheng-koaN2, chi2-u7 chiuN2 chit-e5 Khun-hong, si7 kim--e5, gin5--e5, po2-poe3 ni-ni, na2-chun2 ou7-hioh8 phang5 chin-chu lai5 chiuN2 chit e5 kiaN2. Ia7 chu7-se3 ui7 Khun-hong io chit8 e5 sim-pu7-a2. M7-si7 ui7 bo5 chiN5 lai5 io, si7 ui7 ai3 u7 phoaN7, ai3 chit8 tui3 kiaN2 khah nau7-jiat8. Chit e5 sim-pu7-a2 ia7-si7 siong-tong e5 mng5-hong e5 chhian-kim, tai7-ke si7 se3-kau e5 peng5-iu2. Kau3 toa7-han3 ia7 u7 khi3 thak8 lu2-chu2 ko-tiong. SeN-choe3 ia7-si7 chin sui2, chin u7 ta-ke-ian5. Chhut-si3 chiu7-si7 pai3-put8-a2 lang5, ta-ke si7 jiat8-sim e5 chhai3-kou, sou2-i2 kin-sui5 ta-ke sio-hiuN liam7-keng, pai3-put8 tak8-hang7 to chin koan3-si3. Chhai3-iu2 lai5-ong2 ia7 e7-chu2 chhai3-toh. Siong5-siong5 kin ta-ke khi3 sui5-hiuN. Ni5-cheh chhoe-koe2 pak8-chang3, hau3 mng5-khau2, pan7 seng-le2, tian7-chiu2, poah8-poe ku3 li2 kong2 kiaN7-kiaN7 to e7. It-hoat tit ta-ke thiaN3. Kin-ni5 26 hoe3 lah, chu7 kui2-na7-ni5 cheng5 in ta-ke chiu7 beh ka7 i choe3 toa7-lang5, na7-si7 m7-chai an2-choaN2 e7 bo5 Khun-hong e5 ian5. Sim-pu7-a2 e5 mia5 seN3 Li2 mia5 Siu3-chhun, khi3 hou7 khoaN3-mia7-e5 khoaN3, ka7 i thiah ji7-sou3 kong2 ¡§Li2¡¨, Li2 si7 li2-a2, tho5-li2 put-gian5 ha7 chu7 seng5 ke , i3-su3 si7 kong2 tho5-a2, li2-a2 kau3 si5 na7 sek8 m7-bian2 hou-kio3, lang5 chu7-jian5 e7 lai5 chhin-kin7, e7-bin7 bo5 lou7 ia7 e7 piN3 u7 lou7. ¡§Siu3¡¨ si7 siu3-khi3, chhut-lui7 poat8-chui7, tok8-chhut bo5 lang5 e7-tit kap i pi2 ui5-chi ¡§Siu3.¡¨ ¡§Chhun¡¨ si7 chhun-thiN, ban7-but8 to hian2-chhut eng5-hian2, puh-ge5 thou3-iN2 bou7-seng7, chhun ni5-ni5 chhun, b